<item>
            <title>[LU-4868] Test failure on test suite replay-single, subtest test_80a</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-4868</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for Bob Glossman &amp;lt;bob.glossman@intel.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;http://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/6474aae8-bcba-11e3-b54d-52540035b04c&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/6474aae8-bcba-11e3-b54d-52540035b04c&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This looks a bit like &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-4658&quot; title=&quot;Test failure on test suite replay-single, subtest test_80a creation failed &quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-4658&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-4658&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, but that has been fixed.  I suspect a recent change is causing similar symptoms.  A search in maloo shows only few recent instances, a couple in April, a couple in March.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The sub-test test_80a failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;creation failed&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Info required for matching: replay-single 80a&lt;/p&gt;</description>
